ActCanadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety Act
PrecisRe-appointment of PHILLIP RAYMOND GERMAIN of Regina, Saskatchewan, as a governor of the Council of the Canadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety, being the nominee of the Lieutenant Governor in Council of the Province of Saskatchewan, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years.
